name: Evening Jogging
description: The never ending animated horror film. Part of the Death Fairy Tales loops series. Digital cutout animation by Kajetan Obarski (Kiszkiloszki); 2021; silent; mp4; 1500px1500px. The Death Fairy character was created in 2015 and went viral all around the www. This episode of DFT is based on many of the very first animations from the series and was freshly reanimated.
